title: Black Label Society - Skullage  mp3 320k
description:
Black Label Society - Skullage  mp3 320k  What we got.....    Skullage is a compilation/live album of Zakk Wylde's Black Label Society, although the first song is from Pride and Glory and the second is from Book of Shadows. Some versions also come with a bonus DVD.

This is the third compilation released to document Zakk Wylde's catalogue, the first being the promotional-only No More Tears E.P., followed by Kings of Damnation 98-04 in 2005.
